description:
In this video, we're going to sing our favorite christian songs! Whether you're a longtime karaoke fan or this is your first time, we'll have a lot of fun singing along in this fun and chill video!
If you're looking for a fun and easy way to spend a few minutes, then check out this karaoke video! We'll take you through all the songs you love, and have a lot of fun doing it! Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned singer, this is the video for you!

Songwriters: Thomas Mosie Lister
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube Channel
